{
  "stem": "3658.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they used to put on their tallis, that's their shawl, their prayer shawls, and sort of go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was greeting you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's very, very nice feeling between the peoples.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they must have told the elders of the town, the community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's always--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A council.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was there a Jewish council?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well there was for the Jewish affairs, like for the synagogue and for the anything to do with that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would have notified them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were definitely told that we will be taken at a certain day, which was about a week or so they gave us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or two days, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know it was panic stations when it happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all packed, and everybody, the whole town was packing up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was predominately a Jewish town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So most people, really--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the town were moving out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were moving out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the non-Jewish people that were in town were looking after all the possessions, whatever anybody gave them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was life before the war that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that the respect for the-- was there between the two peoples, because I do remember very vividly, for instance, our next door neighbors and at school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't forget, I mean, we did mix.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't just go with Jewish people to school, we went with everybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a big-- you know, mixed, we went boys and girls were together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was nothing-- and the Jewish boys and girls mixed like they were brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, there was no-- I didn't feel it personally, and I'm sure others didn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mind you, we were-- only difference was that we had payos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did too.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
